Description: Post-processing tools for HiFiMagnet/Feel++ simulations
 python_hifimagnetParaview is a comprehensive Python package that provides
 automated post-processing capabilities for electromagnetics and
 thermomechanics simulations. It integrates with Paraview to enable batch
 processing of simulation exports.
 .
 Key features:
  * Statistical Analysis: Compute descriptive statistics per PointData/CellData
  * Histogram Generation: Create histograms for field distributions
  * Visualization: Generate automated views with customizable colormaps
  * Plot Extraction: Extract 1D plots along radial, axial, or angular coords
  * Multi-format Support: Process Feel++ exports, Ansys VTK files, etc.
  * Comparison Tools: Compare results between different geometries
  * CSV Export: All computed data saved in CSV format for further analysis
 .
 Supports 3D, 2D, and axisymmetric geometries.
